    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏简介</h2>《伏魔之境》(Demon Suppression Realm) 是日醉夜的狗制作发行的一款卡牌类Roguelite游戏,游戏主要玩法是以为牌组构建为基础的卡牌战斗。该作将传统的卡牌构建及Roguelite玩法结合在一起。玩家需要在游戏中构建出独一无二的牌组，在这片奇幻的黑暗大陆中冒险，并挑战未知的魔物。在游戏中有上百中不同的战斗卡牌，几十种能帮助玩家冒险的圣物。在游戏中你除了会遇到不同强度的战斗外，还会触发各种精彩的遭遇事件。在面对不同的事件当中都会有随机生成的选择，玩家的每一次选择都是对玩家的冒险造成影响。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在这片奇幻的黑暗大陆中，你可以在四位个性鲜明的角色当中选择其中一位进行冒险！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/17ee0f5cde5d86702f6fb55a982a517e.poster.avif?t=1723865877\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/17ee0f5cde5d86702f6fb55a982a517e.webm?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>利用好每个角色不同的特性与机制来打败你所遇到的魔物！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/39c03e3a3f3f85a0b6e93334089650ba.poster.avif?t=1723865877\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/39c03e3a3f3f85a0b6e93334089650ba.webm?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/39c03e3a3f3f85a0b6e93334089650ba.mp4?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>除了尽力战胜魔物以外，你还可以在大陆中不同的地区偶遇到不同的人或事！<br><br></li><li><strong>你可以探索充满未知的天然洞穴</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/e713b9f96333aed723e25f57b1e122e9.poster.avif?t=1723865877\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/e713b9f96333aed723e25f57b1e122e9.webm?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/e713b9f96333aed723e25f57b1e122e9.mp4?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>你也可以在朋克旅馆中小憩一会儿</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/9969fe285274865bb25132cd78e63665.poster.avif?t=1723865877\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/9969fe285274865bb25132cd78e63665.webm?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/9969fe285274865bb25132cd78e63665.mp4?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><strong>还可以在商店中购买你所需要的物资</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/5cd599940f8bbad7c5c4ae80608d3e06.avif?t=1723865877\" width=600 height=336 /></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创新设计</h2><strong>相较于传统卡牌肉鸽游戏《伏魔之境》做了以下微创新</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>游戏的推进形式使用半开放型地图探索，取代了传统的单一路线选择<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/f332209756004a83c32a2a42ce7e27cb.poster.avif?t=1723865877\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/f332209756004a83c32a2a42ce7e27cb.webm?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/f332209756004a83c32a2a42ce7e27cb.mp4?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>在游戏的构筑系统上，除了普通的卡牌构筑以外，还增加了额外的构筑系统<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>角色技能系统<br></li><li>角色卡牌克制适配系统<br></li><li>角色基础属性系统</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/277c7a1d0e50b367bf49042b686d3fa2.poster.avif?t=1723865877\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/277c7a1d0e50b367bf49042b686d3fa2.webm?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112000/extras/277c7a1d0e50b367bf49042b686d3fa2.mp4?t=1723865877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>总之在这款游戏中你可以得到传统肉鸽卡牌没有的新体验！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快来这一片奇幻的大陆中冒险吧！我的勇者！</strong></h2></li></ul>",
